---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---
<section class="section-shell section-shell--dark service-cta">
  <div class="shell-inner service-cta__inner">
    <div class="service-cta__content">
      <h2 class="service-cta__title">Cần phân tích riêng cho lô đất cụ thể?</h2>
      <p class="service-cta__desc">
        Mô tả vị trí, diện tích, mục đích sử dụng — nhận đánh giá pháp lý
        và đối chiếu quy hoạch phân khu trong 24 giờ.
      </p>
      <ul class="service-cta__list">
        <li>
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M13.5 4.5L6 12 2.5 8.5" stroke="#4ade80" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          Đối chiếu quy hoạch 1/2.000 chính thức
        </li>
        <li>
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M13.5 4.5L6 12 2.5 8.5" stroke="#4ade80" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          Kiểm tra đất hạn chế: quốc phòng, lâm nghiệp, hành lang
        </li>
        <li>
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M13.5 4.5L6 12 2.5 8.5" stroke="#4ade80" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          Đánh giá vị trí so với ga đường sắt, trục giao thông
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="service-cta__action">
      <a class="service-cta__btn" href="#lead-form">
        Gửi yêu cầu phân tích
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
      </a>
      <p class="service-cta__note">Phản hồi trong 24 giờ làm việc</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .service-cta__inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .service-cta__title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .service-cta__desc {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.5vw, 1.05rem);
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    max-width: 520px;
  }

  .service-cta__list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.6rem;
  }

  .service-cta__list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .service-cta__list svg {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .service-cta__action {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .service-cta__btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 16px 32px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d44809, #a43706);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 100px;
    text-decoration: none;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(212, 72, 9, 0.35);
    transition: all 200ms ease;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .service-cta__btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(212, 72, 9, 0.5);
  }

  .service-cta__note {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .service-cta__inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .service-cta__desc {
      max-width: none;
    }

    .service-cta__list {
      align-items: center;
    }

    .service-cta__action {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .service-cta__btn {
      width: 100%;
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>
